OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be another warm day. It
OL,6,Fwill stay dry through much of the day
OL,7,Fwith bright or sunny spells.
OL,8,
OL,9,CTonight:FDry with some brightness at
OL,10,Ffirst before rain spreads northeast
OL,11,Fthrough the evening and overnight,
OL,12,Fbecoming dry with clear spells by
OL,13,Fmorning.
OL,14,
OL,15,CSaturday:FIt will be dry and warm
OL,16,Fthrough the day with some prolonged
OL,17,Fbright or sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
