OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FWarm
OL,6,Ffrom Sunday to Tuesday with some
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells, chance of some
OL,8,Frain later on Sunday. Perhaps a bit
OL,9,Fcloudier and cooler on Tuesday.
